description: Russian Language Pack for AnySoftKeyboard This is a Cyrillic expansion pack for AnySoftKeyboard. Install AnySoftKeyboard first, and then select the desired layout from AnySoftKeyboard Settings->Keyboards menu. This pack contains Cyrillic and phonetic Russian keyboard layouts, physical keyboard mapping and dictionary. Search for AnySoftKeyboard on Google Play. . . https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.menny.android.anysoftkeyboard
